      <p>Part of the BBN Terms of Service[LINK] require that our members contact each other through the website for all posted projects. If, through the course of business, members develop a professional relationship such that a developer chooses to directly contract with a contractor rather than engaging in a bidding process, then that falls outside the BBN purview.</p>
