      <p>If there is a user who you don't wish to be able to send messages to you through BBN or who you don't wish to be able to bid on projects you post, you can ignore them. The "Ignore" link is located under the user's profile picture on their company profile page. Clicking the Ignore link will take you to a list of people you are currently ignoring. Use the "go back" link or simply hit the back button on your browser to return to the larger EPS site.</p>
