      <p>BBN is a central marketplace for projects and contractors in the building industry. Failure to pay on the part of a project owner is outside of the purview of this site and we accept no liability for such a failure of payment.</p>
      <p>Through BBN's User Review system, project owners can alert the community to unprofessional conduct such as failure to complete contracted work as described in the User Review FAQ[LINK].</p>
